com.velocitypowered.api.command

Interface Command


  • public interface Command
    Represents a command that can be executed by a CommandSource, such as a Player or the console.

    • Method Summary

      • hasPermission

        default boolean hasPermission(CommandSource source,
                              String[] args)
        Tests to check if the source has permission to use this command with the provided args.

        If this method returns false, the handling will be forwarded onto the players current server.

        Parameters:
        source - the source of the command
        args - the arguments for this command
        Returns:
        whether the source has permission
